- cs.TL (Type Theory) is another possible category as the paper deals with pure type systems and their embeddings. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the properties of a logical framework, which can be relevant to software engineering. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the least likely category as the paper does not mention anything related to machine learning.
